    "title": "SOP: 重启 Ops API 并验证健康",
    "content": "1) mkdir -p logs\n2) pkill -f \"python -m scripts.ops_api_server\" || true\n3) nohup python -m scripts.ops_api_server --env dev --host 127.0.0.1 --port 18082 > logs/ops_api_server.log 2>&1 &\n4) curl http://127.0.0.1:18082/healthz",
